Vic Shadez Serves Up *Hors D’oeuvres*—A Taste of What’s to Come** 

New Jersey’s own Vic Shadez returns with *Hors D’oeuvres*, a finely curated EP that sets the stage for the feast ahead. This four-track offering, produced entirely by GIDDT-AVM, is more than just music—it’s an experience designed for hip-hop’s most refined palates. 

Seasoned to perfection, *Hors D’oeuvres* delivers lyricism simmered to a depth of flavor only a true chef can achieve. No filler. No artificial ingredients. Just raw, organic hip-hop—GMO-free and packed with soul-nourishing vibrations. 

This is just the appetizer. The main course is coming. Stay hungry.
